author: Toby Gannon, The Sun
title: WWE’s sex tape problem is getting worse | New York Post
text:
WWE star Maria has become the latest wrestler to apparently have X-rated photos leaked online.
The pictures circulating online appear to show Maria — real name Maria Louise Kanellis-Bennett — posing naked. Several explicit photos have been posted, showing a woman taking selfies in a bathroom and on a bed.
Maria is married to fellow wrestler Mike Bennett.
The pictures come after WWE superstar Paige and ex-wrestler Kaitlyn had explicit images and videos posted on the internet . The X-rated images appear to show Kaitlyn, real name Celeste Bonin, in a series of nude selfies.
Paige claimed her pics were private and were shared without her consent .
One of the clips featured the 24-year-old with two of her male wrestling colleagues . Another video features Paige performing a solo act with a sex toy, another engaging in oral sex, while there are at least three other videos in which she is seen having sex with men.
A post shared by Maria Kanellis-Bennett (@mariakanellis) on Mar 11, 2017 at 3:53pm PST 
Paige is engaged to ex-WWE star Alberto Del Rio, who jumped into the ring and proposed in October last year. In August, the WWE suspended Paige for 30 days for a violation of the company’s anti-drugs wellness policy.
Maria began her WWE career in 2004 after competing in the Raw Diva Search.
She came closest to winning a Divas Championship in 2008, but was beaten by then-champion Michelle McCool in the title match. In 2014, she married Bennett in Chicago after being engaged for two years.
